                    <h2>What makes Stirling a great student city?</h2>
                    <div><ul>
<li><strong>Location</strong> – Stirling is for adventurous students, close to the must-see Scottish cities of Glasgow and Edinburgh.</li>
<li><strong>History</strong> – uncover an incredible history preserved in Stirling’s streets, castles and exhibited at The Engine Shed.</li>
<li><strong>Price</strong> – the cost of living here is one of the lowest in the UK, so you’ll be able to do more with your money.</li>
<li><strong>Food</strong> – Scotland is famous for its food; discover excellent international restaurants and Asian supermarkets here.</li>
<li><strong>Entertainment</strong> – from pubs and music venues to a bowling alley and multiplex cinema, you’ll always be entertained.</li>
</ul>
</div>
